4e81d6c

body:
Looking into it more deeply, this actually looks like a problem with particular x86 architectures that existed before the move. I wasn't able to reproduce it on my machine, but I've checked in this change which I hope should fix it:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/4e81d6cc877ba4a56196bbdd8d4e09ab7f7b8412

Can you give it a try and let me know? Thanks!
